	<refsect1>
		<title>Description</title>
		<para>
			This manual page documents briefly the <command>&package;</command> command.
		</para>
		<para>
			<command>&package;</command> is a tool to build Debian packages in an isolated environment.
			To achieve isolation, <command>systemd-nspawn</command> is used internally.
		</para>
	</refsect1>

